# QA UAT Agent — cache directory
# Cache is regenerated from evidence/ and recorded sessions; do not commit.
# Exception: ui_maps/ is kept tracked because it serves as a reproducibility
# baseline for the supported screen catalogue (committed deliberately).
# Exception: discovered_selectors.json.schema — the schema reference file IS
# committed so developers know the expected format.
*.json
!.gitignore
!discovered_selectors.json.schema
